structure.unit: ESCAPES, FUGITIVES FROM JUSTICE, AND EXTRADITION

law.history: Repealed 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 135, sec. 30. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1930, 1931.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Arrest and delivery of person guilty of felony in another state.
